chunk_content: Recent infection testing algorithm (RITA) 98 PEPFAR-support Standard definitions of DSD and TA-SDI apply. definition: For HTS services, direct service delivery includes: ongoing procurement of critical HTS related T commodities such as rapid HIV test kits or requisite materials (lancets, capillary tubes), samples and E S materials for proficiency testing, other HIV diagnostic commodities, or funding for salaries of HIV T testing service providers including counselors, laboratory technicians, program managers, and/or I N community health workers. Staff who are responsible for the completeness and quality of routine G patient records (paper or electronic) can be counted here; however, staff who exclusively fulfill MOH and donor reporting requirements cannot be counted.
